text_2201__089DAD8D:
	.string "There should be some {SPECIAL_02_PAR_1}{SPECIAL_02_PAR_1}Minish{SPECIAL_02_PAR_1}{END} living here{NL}in this forest.{NL}Eh? Who are the {SPECIAL_02_PAR_1}{SPECIAL_02_PAR_1}Minish{SPECIAL_02_PAR_1}{END}? Ah, yes,{NL}how silly of me!{NL}You humans call them {DOUBLE_QUOTE}{SPECIAL_02_PAR_1}{SPECIAL_02_PAR_1}Picori{SPECIAL_02_PAR_1}{END},{DOUBLE_QUOTE} but they{NL}refer to themselves as the {SPECIAL_02_PAR_1}{SPECIAL_02_PAR_1}Minish{SPECIAL_02_PAR_1}{END}!{NL}Strange how, in the world of humans,{NL}only this forest has kept the name...{NL}Anyhow, deep in the forest they built a{NL}tiny village, where many now live.{NL}But if we{SINGLE_QUOTE}re to enter the village, we{SINGLE_QUOTE}ll{NL}have to make you a touch smaller first.{NL}Look for a tree stump. Then, I can{NL}shrink you to the size of the {DOUBLE_QUOTE}{SPECIAL_02_PAR_1}{SPECIAL_02_PAR_1}Picori{SPECIAL_02_PAR_1}{END}.{DOUBLE_QUOTE}{END}"


text_2202__089DAF88:
	.string "{SPECIAL_03_PAR_2}{END}{BYTE_92}{SPECIAL_04_PAR_2}{BYTE_10}{END}Hold on for a moment, my boy! We{SINGLE_QUOTE}ve{NL}stumbled across something important!{NL}The world of the {SPECIAL_02_PAR_1}{SPECIAL_02_PAR_1}Minish{SPECIAL_02_PAR_1}{END} is very small.{NL}You{SINGLE_QUOTE}re far too big to meet them now.{NL}Eh? Who are the {SPECIAL_02_PAR_1}{SPECIAL_02_PAR_1}Minish{SPECIAL_02_PAR_1}{END}? Ah, yes! Silly{NL}me! Allow me to explain...{NL}You humans call them {DOUBLE_QUOTE}{SPECIAL_02_PAR_1}{SPECIAL_02_PAR_1}Picori{SPECIAL_02_PAR_1}{END},{DOUBLE_QUOTE} but they{NL}refer to themselves as the {SPECIAL_02_PAR_1}{SPECIAL_02_PAR_1}Minish{SPECIAL_02_PAR_1}{END}!{NL}Strange how, in the world of humans,{NL}only this forest has kept that name...{NL}Anyhow, deep in the forest they built a{NL}tiny village, where many now live.{NL}But if we{SINGLE_QUOTE}re to enter the village, we{SINGLE_QUOTE}ll{NL}have to make you a touch smaller first.{NL}Look at that. At first glance, it{NL}appears to be a mere stump, yes?{NL}No! That stump is a {SPECIAL_02_PAR_1}{SPECIAL_03_PAR_2}portal{SPECIAL_02_PAR_1}{END} used by{NL}people long ago to adjust their size!{NL}With my help, you can use it to {SPECIAL_02_PAR_1}{SPECIAL_03_PAR_2}shrink{NL}down to Minish size{SPECIAL_02_PAR_1}{END}.{NL}Just stand on the stump and press {SPECIAL_0C_PAR_1}{SPECIAL_03_PAR_2}{NL}to shrink.{NL}To return to normal, stand next to the{NL}stump and press {SPECIAL_0C_PAR_1}{SPECIAL_03_PAR_2}.{NL}Get me up there, and we{SINGLE_QUOTE}ll give{NL}it a try.{END}"


text_2203__089DB30D:
	.string "Welcome to the world through the{NL}eyes of the Minish!{NL}Now, aren{SINGLE_QUOTE}t you glad you saved me?{NL}No need to thank me, though!{NL}Portals that reduce your size are {SPECIAL_02_PAR_1}{SPECIAL_03_PAR_2}all{NL}around, in different shapes and sizes{SPECIAL_02_PAR_1}{END}.{SPECIAL_02_PAR_1}{SPECIAL_03_PAR_2}{NL}{SPECIAL_02_PAR_1}{END}If you want to return to normal, stand{NL}next to a portal and press {SPECIAL_0C_PAR_1}{SPECIAL_03_PAR_2}.{NL}But there is one thing you must know:{NL}{SPECIAL_02_PAR_1}{SPECIAL_03_PAR_2}being Minish-sized is full of dangers{SPECIAL_02_PAR_1}{END}!{NL}Mere puddles at your normal size{NL}are bottomless swamps to the Minish.{NL}And as your companion, if anything bad{NL}happens to you, it happens to me, too!{NL}So proceed with caution, my lad! If not{NL}for your sake, then for my own!{END}"

